Use this to create AWS Lambda functions that will turn on and off ec2 instances. 
You can use schedules for that using AWS Event Bridge.
Usage:
Use each of the .py scripts for the lambda functions.
Use the JSON file for creating an IAM role using the IAM policy specified in the JSON file, and attach it to the Lambda function. 

More info can be found here: https://repost.aws/knowledge-center/start-stop-lambda-eventbridge